# 02 · Color Palette

*Warm, editorial, and a little feral. Drawn from the mood board: amber drips, 70s interior warmth, cream of soft-serve, retro rust and burnt orange. This is not a clean-brand-beige palette — it has teeth.*

> **v2 update:** Drizzle (#C4711A) replaced by Rust (#E8622A) as primary brand accent. Ember (#C44B1B) added as depth partner. Algae and Feral demoted to named future-SKU reserves. Walnut hex corrected to #3D1F0D.
