| Roast | `#1C1410` | Primary text · wordmark base · all SKUs |
| Walnut | `#3D1F0D` | Footer depth · secondary dark · body text on cream |
| Rust | `#E8622A` | Primary brand accent — wordmark color, stripe, wave on Original SKU · retro-burnt, shelf-popping |
