# 05 · Brand Voice

## Voice Principles

| Principle | What it means in practice |
| --- | --- |
| Confident, not arrogant | "We didn't reinvent peanut butter." We just made it make sense as a topping. |
| Playful, not silly | Wit is always in service of appetite. Never in service of a joke. |
| Clean, not clinical | "Two ingredients." Not "a simple, clean, whole-food snacking solution with minimal processing." |
| Premium, no preaching | No macros in the headline. No lecturing. Lead with desire. |

## Words We Never Say

> Superfood · Clean eating · Guilt-free · Wholesome · Artisanal · Nourishing · Snack responsibly · Plant-based · Mindful
> 

